Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.27,0:00:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the banner even?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.64,0:00:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Are the flowers in place?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.38,0:00:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...by which I mean\Ncompletely out of view.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.55,0:00:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure\Ndragons don't like flowers...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.52,0:00:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about the ceremonial\NDragon-Fire Flame of Friendship?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.19,0:00:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it still flaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.46,0:00:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, everything\Nlooks great!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.16,0:00:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're getting yourself\Nworked up for no reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.69,0:00:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I have lots of reasons!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.46,0:00:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I wrote them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.46,0:00:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh.. You've been hanging around\NTwilight for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.36,0:00:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.13,0:00:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Reason number one:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.13,0:00:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I invited Dragon Lord\NEmber to Ponyville today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.57,0:00:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Reason two, the Dragon\NLord is a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.04,0:00:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Reason three: she's coming here\Nto learn more about friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.14,0:00:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,According to Ember's letters,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.58,0:00:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the dragons are\Ntrying to be friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.48,0:00:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,but competing is\Nin their nature
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.88,0:00:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's leading to\Nmore and more fights.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.88,0:00:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Which brings me to\Nreason number four:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.09,0:00:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dragon Lord wants my advice!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.25,0:00:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And as the new official\NEquestrian Friendship Ambassador
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.59,0:00:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to the dragons, I\Ncan't let her down.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.26,0:00:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you feel a\Nlot of pressure,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.03,0:01:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but you've got this, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.73,0:01:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.83,0:01:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want things\Nto be perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.67,0:01:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp!] Thorax... you're in Ponyville!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I am, silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.67,0:01:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You invited me and I'm not one\Nto back out of an invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.18,0:01:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.18,0:01:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Starlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.41,0:01:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight: Heyyy...\NStarlight: Hello....
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.52,0:01:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thorax: Oooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.42,0:01:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you\Ndid all this for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.19,0:01:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Great banner!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.32,0:01:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Love the stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.96,0:01:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this flame thingy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.69,0:01:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.69,0:01:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You invited Thorax\Nover to Ponyville
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.83,0:01:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,on the same day as Ember!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.46,0:01:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.07,0:01:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't seem\Nlike a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.30,0:01:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you going to\Nentertain them both?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.34,0:01:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.68,0:02:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I completely forgot\NThorax wrote
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.48,0:02:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and said he needed to talk\Nand I told him to come over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.98,0:02:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't realize it was the\Nsame day I invited Ember!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.39,0:02:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I gonna do!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.59,0:02:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe they'll\Nlike each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.69,0:02:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.79,0:02:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ember is tough and\Nself-assured and intimidating.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And Thorax is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.50,0:02:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, I'm so glad\Nyou invited me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.17,0:02:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You are one of my closest,\Nnicest, most caring,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,most understanding\Nfriends ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.11,0:02:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Is that ice in the\Nshape of a dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.71,0:02:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I see\Nyour point.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.91,0:02:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They might not\Nget each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.25,0:03:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Or worse, they'll\Nhate each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.58,0:03:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And if the leader of the\NChangelings and the Dragon Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.75,0:03:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,get into a fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.69,0:03:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I could be responsible\Nfor starting a war
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.15,0:03:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,that could ruin\NEquestria as we know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.63,0:03:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that\Nwon't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.17,0:03:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, pull it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.57,0:03:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So... Thorax...\Neverything good with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.81,0:03:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, honestly, no, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.28,0:03:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I have indigestion, not\Nsure if it's the new diet,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.55,0:03:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,or stress or maybe it's both.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.95,0:03:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.22,0:03:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It really could be both.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.49,0:03:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And it might be affecting\Nmy sleeping, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.89,0:03:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight: Uh oh..\NThorax: I'm a real tosser and\Nturner these-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.66,0:03:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like you\Nreally need to unwind!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.79,0:03:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Er.. how about a er.. a trip\Nto the castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.03,0:03:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't miss that view!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.70,0:03:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.30,0:03:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a\Npersonal tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.37,0:03:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Are.. aren't you coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.24,0:04:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...I'm just gonna grab some\Nice cream for us and catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.31,0:04:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.09,0:04:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon Lord Ember, as the\Nofficial Equestrian Friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.13,0:04:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambassador for the Dragonlands\Nand for Ponyville,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.96,0:04:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Spike of Ponyville,\Nwelcome you to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.74,0:04:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta work on my\Nofficial speech..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,OK. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh heh.. right. The hug thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.14,0:04:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.58,0:04:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This place has a lot of colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.45,0:04:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,In the Dragonlands, everything's\Njust rocks or the color of ash.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.55,0:04:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,ACHOO!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.42,0:04:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's probably why..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.13,0:04:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.03,0:04:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'm Starlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.30,0:04:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight Glimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.20,0:05:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.17,0:05:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.50,0:05:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm.. really gonna have to get\Nused to these pony names.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.24,0:05:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots of "lights"\Nand shiny things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.84,0:05:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Er.. so where is Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.71,0:05:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,She's in her castle--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.71,0:05:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,OH!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.31,0:05:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We should go visit her then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.81,0:05:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Part of friendship is saying\Nhi to your friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.38,0:05:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.15,0:05:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,well yeah.. but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.79,0:05:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're making weird noises.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.52,0:05:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a stomach ache?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.16,0:05:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] I think I feel one coming on..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know what us dragons\Nsay: push past the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.70,0:05:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.37,0:05:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Or.. we could stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Or I could go without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.31,0:05:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh heh heh. Ah.\NI like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.52,0:05:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, they're not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.55,0:05:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I...I said, it's\Nall clean in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.13,0:06:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Er.. you must be hungry\Nfrom your travels.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.23,0:06:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, I'd love to present\Nyou with an official
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.20,0:06:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Friendship Welcome Banquet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is something friends do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I could get used to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.95,0:06:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually that's\Nnot food...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragons love gems.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.42,0:06:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, but you're telling\NTwilight what happened
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,to her wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.29,0:06:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Just keep her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, yeah, enjoy\Nall the crystal... things..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.66,0:06:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.97,0:06:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought this was an\Nofficial friendship banquet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Just gotta use the\Nlittle dragon's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.54,0:06:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is my comfy chair\Nfor fictional reads.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.24,0:06:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my studying chair
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,because the hard\Nback keeps me awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.69,0:07:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Spike! I'm so\Nglad you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This castle visit\Nis getting weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight really likes chairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.46,0:07:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. What happened to the ice cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.83,0:07:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Oh, right!\NUh, they ran out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm really sorry, but I\Ngotta borrow Twilight quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.72,0:07:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.08,0:07:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Be right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.94,0:07:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But we didn't get to talk yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ember's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.48,0:07:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I know; I saw you coming\Nand had to distract Thorax
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.32,0:07:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,by showing him chairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.72,0:07:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you bring Ember to\Nthe castle of all places?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.16,0:07:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.16,0:07:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ember was asking for you, Thorax\Nwants to talk with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.30,0:07:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,we need to switch places!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They might be\Ngetting suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.93,0:07:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All we have to do is make both\NThorax and Ember feel special
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.17,0:07:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and keep them apart\Nfor a few more hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.34,0:07:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.37,0:07:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! What's happening!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.73,0:07:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah..!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's the map!\NIt's calling... you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.15,0:08:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, you also have to\Nsolve a friendship problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.83,0:08:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The map is calling me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.13,0:08:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... amazing! The map is\Nreally reaching out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a good time,\NI get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.97,0:08:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight: Spike, are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.57,0:08:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ember's eaten all of\NTwilight's decorations and--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.01,0:08:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Hey Twilight. Heh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.68,0:08:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Glowing map.. [gulp] glowing spikes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.38,0:08:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.18,0:08:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I KNOW!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.72,0:08:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,At least your friendship\Nproblem is in Ponyville?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, OK, to pull this\Noff, I'm going to need
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.26,0:08:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,both of you to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.73,0:08:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You two need to keep\NEmber and Thorax separate
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.40,0:08:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,while I\Nget ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.26,0:08:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean find the\Nfriendship problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.33,0:08:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:08:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Go easy on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.77,0:08:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm under a lot\Nof pressure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.64,0:08:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Friendship Problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.17,0:09:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Anypony got a\Nfriendship problem here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.58,0:09:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Any problems to solve?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Friendship problems?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Friendship Problems!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.02,0:09:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Anypony got a\Nfriendship problem here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.35,0:09:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No? OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.29,0:09:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Uch. Well I think vanilla\Nstrawberry cream is overused!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.63,0:09:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.23,0:09:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.53,0:09:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I mean, what seems\Nto be the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.51,0:09:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ember, there you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.01,0:09:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,OK... right,\Nmore pony hugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.11,0:09:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,How's your trip to\NPonyville so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.41,0:09:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm certainly learning\Na lot about friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.12,0:09:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea it was polite\Nto decorate your walls
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.52,0:09:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,in your friends' favorite foods.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.06,0:09:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh heh. Oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.56,0:09:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd Spike and Starlight go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.29,0:09:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm being avoided.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:09:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.63,0:10:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No! They're just making\Nsure everything is perfect
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.93,0:10:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,for your welcome party later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.07,0:10:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,In the meantime, how about\NI show you around town?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.64,0:10:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.64,0:10:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't exactly learn\Nabout friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.51,0:10:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,if I don't make new friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.99,0:10:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.40,0:10:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh.. Hey Thorax...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.25,0:10:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Um. Twilight and Spike had some\Nboring official paperwork
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,to deal with, so looks like\Nyou and I get to hang out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.29,0:10:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you like to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.66,0:10:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wanted to\Ntalk with Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.46,0:10:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he'd be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.17,0:10:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh you will, but first how\Nabout we grab a bite to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.50,0:10:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. Well you know, now that you've said\Nit, I am a little hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.14,0:10:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a dining\Nroom in the castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.04,0:10:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.41,0:10:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,... I mean yeah, but\Nthat's castle food.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.21,0:10:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want the good\Nstuff, we gotta go to town.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.05,0:10:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,... and that's why you should\Nnever let cupcake flavors
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:10:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,get in the way of\Nyour friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:11:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. I guess I never thought of it\Nthat way. Thanks, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on! Glow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.73,0:11:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thorax: Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.97,0:11:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Done with your boring\Npaper work I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.74,0:11:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha ha...! A-huh.. A-huh..?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.67,0:11:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, heh heh. I am done with whatever\NStarlight says I was doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.31,0:11:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thorax wanted to get\Nout of the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought coming to town was\Na really, really great idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.55,0:11:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well! Maybe now we can talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.22,0:11:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ssssure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.32,0:11:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave you guys to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, I want to say\Nthank you for having me over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.30,0:11:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in a bit of a\Nleadership pickle
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and I could use\Nsome advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.90,0:11:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I definitely want to help\Nyou out as quickly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.54,0:11:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's my problem: there's this\Nrenegade group of changelings
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,who still feed off of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.44,0:11:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I said, "Hey, let's\Nnot do that anymore," they say,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.21,0:11:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hey this is how we've\Nbeen doing things
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,for hundreds of years-"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-but it's like they don't\Nwant to even though
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:11:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the leader and I\Nasked politely...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.89,0:12:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Ember, daughter of Torch,\Nwinner of the Gauntlet of Fire
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.13,0:12:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and lord of all dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.61,0:12:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually when I do that, the\Ndragons are eager to meet me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.61,0:12:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not how\Nponies make friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.61,0:12:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh... I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.12,0:12:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a weird friendship\Nthing you ponies do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.36,0:12:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... you guys\Nare in town, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.23,0:12:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you\Ntalking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.40,0:12:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been with\Nme this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.50,0:12:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm Starlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Riiiiight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.54,0:12:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but you\Ncan't blame me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.67,0:12:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You both look and\Nact so much alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.14,0:12:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Both: What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.75,0:13:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And they said to me just\Nkeep saying the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.88,0:13:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You know I think my leadership\Nproblems started in childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.25,0:13:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I must've been three when ...\NThree's a different story --
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.62,0:13:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and you definitely\Ngotta hear it,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.12,0:13:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,but the story about my\Nbrother was when I was two...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.23,0:13:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Or was I one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.49,0:13:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.86,0:13:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I got here first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.03,0:13:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thorax, excuse me for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.04,0:13:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ponies, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.54,0:13:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If I may, I think I can help\Nsolve this.. friendship problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.78,0:13:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You two should sit together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.85,0:13:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You both like the same place;\Nyou both ordered muffins;
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.28,0:13:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,you're both ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.38,0:13:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I think if you made\Na little effort,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.95,0:13:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd find that you\Nhave a .... whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.02,0:13:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, that had to have done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.89,0:13:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on spikes, glow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.13,0:13:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that was\Nreally great advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do you\Nthink I should do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I uh need a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.84,0:14:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Alone. To really come\Nup with great advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.71,0:14:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.64,0:14:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[sigh] Great. No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.35,0:14:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me again...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.85,0:14:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine....
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.92,0:14:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just saying, you're both\Npurple ponies with purple hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You both have cutie marks\Nwith sparkle-y things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.06,0:14:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh. Mine's more of\Na glimmer..! Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.03,0:14:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How is that different?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.16,0:14:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.90,0:14:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you please tell\Nthese two I'm right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.33,0:14:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They look very similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.94,0:14:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Er.. Well, you know, one thing\Nfriends do is let something go
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,when it's upsetting\Nsomepony else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.24,0:14:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.44,0:14:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, who are you to be\Ntelling me about friendship?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.51,0:14:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I've barely seen\Nyou all day!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.58,0:14:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh.. well.. I've seen you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.75,0:14:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you calling me a LIAR!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.05,0:14:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! No one yells\Nat my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.10,0:14:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, get away from the bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually the bear's a changeling\Nand he's quite gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Not anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.38,0:15:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaah! My worst fears are happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.12,0:15:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.73,0:15:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. Back away, Spike, I'm not\Ngoing to let this dragon
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.80,0:15:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,harm a scale on your back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.60,0:15:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You back away! I'm not\Ngoing to let you harm him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.07,0:15:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, did you say you're not\Ngoing to let me harm Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.47,0:15:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.41,0:15:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's what I'm doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.21,0:15:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh..what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.94,0:15:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.58,0:15:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh.. Equestria as we know it is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.61,0:15:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The war that pits\Nchangeling against dragon
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.32,0:15:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,is about to begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.68,0:15:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's all my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,My title of Equestria's\NFriendship Ambassador is a lie--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.36,0:15:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Hey. You guys\Naren't fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.22,0:15:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would we be fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.96,0:16:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I accidentally\Ninvited you both
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,over to Ponyville\Non the same day?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.23,0:16:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Both: So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.00,0:16:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I was trying\Nto keep you apart,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.10,0:16:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,because I didn't\Nthink you'd get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.67,0:16:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.81,0:16:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You thought he wouldn't like me\Njust because I'm a dragon
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.51,0:16:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm bad at friendship?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.71,0:16:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No! Of course not! But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.22,0:16:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, isn't that\Nwhy you're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.95,0:16:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can say I'm bad at friendship;\Nyou can't say it about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.62,0:16:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what? I don't\Nwant to talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.16,0:16:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.96,0:16:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[sigh] I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.53,0:16:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no. It's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.16,0:16:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You thought I'd be too soft\Nand someone like Ember
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,would never respect me, just\Nlike my own changelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.27,0:16:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.54,0:16:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thorax! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.51,0:16:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.04,0:16:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What have I done?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.42,0:17:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.95,0:17:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[sigh] Because I'm having\Ntrouble leading my pack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.56,0:17:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So I don't really\Nwant to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.33,0:17:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you're in charge?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.56,0:17:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ho boy, you need to\Nbe more assertive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.10,0:17:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my problem,\NI don't know how.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.24,0:17:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried asking them to please\Nfollow my directions
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.67,0:17:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and I even offered\Na prize and--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.61,0:17:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,SHH! Stop talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.08,0:17:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.85,0:17:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa. That just\Ngave me chills.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.78,0:17:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you have\Nit in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.22,0:17:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You turned into a\Nbear to defend Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.39,0:17:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. I guess I can be tough when\NI'm defending my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.36,0:17:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But.. when I'm just enforcing my\Nrules, I feel unsure of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.36,0:17:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to\Nbe unsure of.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.46,0:17:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the leader\Nfor a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.57,0:17:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Make a decision and\Nlet it be known
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,that the decision is final.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And if that doesn't\Nwork, turn into a bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.27,0:17:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.71,0:17:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.38,0:17:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's your deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.08,0:18:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think you're\Nso bad at friendship?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.08,0:18:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to\Ntalk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.12,0:18:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.65,0:18:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How else are you gonna\Nsolve your problems?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.89,0:18:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Through feats of strength\Nand fire duels, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.39,0:18:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiyah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.10,0:18:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... how did that help?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.40,0:18:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Crushing another\Ndragon in competition
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.43,0:18:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,establishes my dominance\Nand makes me feel great!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.07,0:18:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, but how do\Nyou think they feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.17,0:18:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Humiliated! Ashamed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.94,0:18:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They probably want to run\Naway and bury themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.31,0:18:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,under a rock and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.95,0:18:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,... never come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.42,0:18:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They're probably sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.18,0:18:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinda low.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.79,0:18:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Definitely not happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.49,0:18:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because that kind of\Ncompetition can divide you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.69,0:18:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And it doesn't get to\Nthe heart of the issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.09,0:18:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Talking about your\Nfeelings does.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.76,0:18:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Achoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.30,0:18:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ach. I think I'm allergic\Nto feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.97,0:18:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You know you don't have to  be\Nsappy or huggy-feely about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.80,0:19:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but you should let your\Nfriends know how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.. I know where\Nwe can start.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.35,0:19:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Spike. Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.45,0:19:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I got there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.79,0:19:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.32,0:19:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.62,0:19:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They probably never\Nwant to see me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.72,0:19:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Or ... they want\Nto see you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.36,0:19:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess what, Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.03,0:19:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. I'm so sorry--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.20,0:19:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,LET ME TALK ABOUT THIS!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.37,0:19:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.53,0:19:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,... mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.30,0:19:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.., that's a good\Nfirst attempt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.67,0:19:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Now maybe try to\Nbe more.. specific?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.41,0:19:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.52,0:19:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,ugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.72,0:19:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,upset!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.05,0:19:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You have every right to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.65,0:19:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I KNOW I DO!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And I know I need to\Ntell you how I feel
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,because my friend, Thorax, said\Nit would make me feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,AND IT DOES!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.90,0:19:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! And I have no\Nproblem telling you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.40,0:19:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,what you did\Nwas wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.63,0:20:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,because my\Nfriend Ember
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.33,0:20:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,is helping me be\Nmore assertive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.17,0:20:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.67,0:20:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.74,0:20:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.97,0:20:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys should be mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.88,0:20:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so worried about\Nhow it could go wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.25,0:20:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't even think about\Nhow it could go right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.55,0:20:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you forgive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.05,0:20:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I really do\Nfeel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So, yeah. I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.39,0:20:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh. Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.74,0:20:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.26,0:20:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohhh.. again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.70,0:20:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! It's finally happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.57,0:20:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I solved a friendship problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.24,0:20:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, you created\Nthe friendship problem
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.37,0:20:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,by not trusting your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.91,0:20:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but then I solved\Nit by learning my lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.41,0:20:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have told\Nmy two friends
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.85,0:20:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,about each other immediately,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.65,0:20:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of assuming\Nthey wouldn't get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.88,0:20:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.39,0:20:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this another part\Nof pony friendship?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.69,0:20:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Telling each other what\Nyou learned all the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.39,0:20:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, pretty much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.63,0:21:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.30,0:21:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike: So! As a\Nshow of unity,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.67,0:21:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I present the Dragon Fire\NFlame of Friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.33,0:21:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,to both Dragon Lord Ember
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.94,0:21:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and Thorax, Leader of\Nthe Changeling Pack.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.81,0:21:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,May the Flame of Friendship\Nburn for eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.18,0:21:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Achoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.45,0:21:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You should have more\Nthings made of rocks.
